## 📈 Erweiterte Features

### 1. Multi-Language Support

```php
// Übersetzungen laden
load_plugin_textdomain('nova-ai', false, dirname(plugin_basename(__FILE__)) . '/languages');

// Custom Prompts pro Sprache
add_filter('nova_ai_system_prompt', function($prompt, $locale) {
    if ($locale === 'de_DE') {
        return 'Du bist ein hilfreicher deutscher AI-Assistant...';
    }
    return $prompt;
}, 10, 2);
```

### 2. Custom Models

```php
// Eigene Modelle hinzufügen
add_filter('nova_ai_available_models', function($models) {
    $models['custom:my-model'] = 'Mein Custom Model';
    return $models;
});
```

### 3. Webhook Integration

```php
// Webhooks für externe Services
add_action('nova_ai_conversation_complete', function($conversation_id, $messages) {
    wp_remote_post('https://your-webhook-url.com', array(
        'body' => json_encode(array(
            'conversation_id' => $conversation_id,
            'messages' => $messages
        ))
    ));
});
```

